      <title>丹麦提高柴油税以资助绿色转型支出</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/denmark-raises-diesel-fuel-tax-to-fund-green-transition-spending</link>
      <description><![CDATA[到 2030 年，丹麦将花费约 50 亿克朗（7.15 亿美元）用于农业部门的绿色转型和其他环保举措，其中部分资金将通过提高燃料税来提供。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/denmark-raises-diesel-fuel-tax-to-fund-green-transition-spending</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 09:18:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
